        {
            "_id": "yGt3DCCx3RRiX2BQ",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneThreeActions.webp",
            "name": "Massacre",
            "sort": 300000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The champions slash mercilessly with their broadswords against enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:27|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+3)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d8+12)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d8+14)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
                },
                "frequency": {
                    "max": 1,
                    "per": "round"
                },
